name: our deepest fear poster
description:
A3 poster, 'Our deepest fear' design.

"Our deepest fear is not that we are inadequate, it's that we are powerful beyond measure. It's our light, not our darkness that most frightens us. We ask ourselves, who am i to be brilliant? Who are you not to be?! You are a child of the universe. Your playing small doesn't serve the world, there is nothing enlightening about shrinking so that other people won't feel insecure around you. We are born to manifest the glory of the universe that is within us. It's not just in some of us, it's in everyone. And as we let our own light shine, we unconciously give other people permission to do the same. And as we are liberated from our own fear, our presence automatically liberates others." - Marianne Williamson
